(I'll head off to the boat
to get ready.)

23
00:02:43,600 --> 00:02:44,800
(Pick you up for diving at 10 PM.)

24
00:02:45,000 --> 00:02:45,720
(See you later.)

25
00:02:52,970 --> 00:02:56,750
[Love you forever]

26
00:02:59,240 --> 00:03:00,700
[Gu Cheng]

27
00:03:08,119 --> 00:03:08,880
I'll be right there.

28
00:03:51,280 --> 00:03:53,080
[President of Anshi Furniture]
(The Yan couple from Anshi Group)

29
00:03:53,080 --> 00:03:54,479
(are discovered embezzling)

30
00:03:54,680 --> 00:03:55,680
[Financial Personnel]
(a significant amount of funds.)

31
00:03:55,694 --> 00:03:57,600
[of Suspected Corruption Commits Suicide]
(The situation is still under review.)

32
00:03:57,600 --> 00:03:59,880
(Recently, there was a suicide
in a neighborhood)

33
00:03:59,880 --> 00:04:01,759
(witnessed by the 14-year-old daughter
of the deceased,)

34
00:04:01,759 --> 00:04:02,520
(Yan.)

35
00:04:02,520 --> 00:04:03,080
(Based on our information,)

36
00:04:03,080 --> 00:04:05,000
(the deceased was connected
to the embezzlement case)

37
00:04:05,000 --> 00:04:06,440
(of Anshi Group.)

38
00:04:06,440 --> 00:04:07,839
(However, due to the lack
of crucial evidence...)

39
00:04:08,000 --> 00:04:08,479
(Mom.)

40
00:04:08,720 --> 00:04:10,479
(I will find the truth.)

41
00:04:14,810 --> 00:04:16,780
[All of Her]

42
00:04:16,800 --> 00:04:18,860
[Episode 1]

43
00:04:19,079 --> 00:04:21,540
[Four years later]

44
00:04:21,559 --> 00:04:23,799
Thank you for attending
the press conference.

45
00:04:24,600 --> 00:04:25,440
Four years ago,

46
00:04:25,839 --> 00:04:27,279
Zejia met an accident.

47
00:04:27,559 --> 00:04:28,799
So, I took on

48
00:04:28,920 --> 00:04:30,000
the role of acting general manager.

49
00:04:30,600 --> 00:04:32,519
Initially, many people looked down on me

50
00:04:32,720 --> 00:04:33,920
and Anshi Group.

51
00:04:34,359 --> 00:04:35,559
Fortunately,

52
00:04:35,799 --> 00:04:36,640
I didn't let down

53
00:04:36,640 --> 00:04:38,720
your trust and support.

54
00:04:39,359 --> 00:04:40,880
Anshi managed
to sail through the hardships.

55
00:04:41,720 --> 00:04:42,560
[Yan Zhen]
This miracle

56
00:04:43,119 --> 00:04:44,720
[General Director of Anshi Group]
was achieved by all of us.

57
00:04:45,359 --> 00:04:46,399
I believe

58
00:04:46,760 --> 00:04:48,760
we will create more miracles.

59
00:04:49,359 --> 00:04:50,559
You're not the largest shareholder here.

60
00:04:50,880 --> 00:04:52,519
I don't think
it's appropriate to say that.

61
00:04:53,239 --> 00:04:53,880
Ms. Yan.

62
00:04:54,040 --> 00:04:55,760
Everyone here
recognized your capability.

63
00:04:55,760 --> 00:04:56,880
But, as you said,

64
00:04:57,160 --> 00:04:57,959
you're an acting general manager.

65
00:04:58,239 --> 00:04:59,519
It's been four years.

66
00:04:59,519 --> 00:05:01,440
It's time to step down, is it not?

67
00:05:02,279 --> 00:05:04,720
By any chance, do you want
to sit on it until retirement?

68
00:05:07,760 --> 00:05:08,959
In this agreement,

69
00:05:09,160 --> 00:05:11,119
Mr. Wang signed his shares over to me.

70
00:05:11,920 --> 00:05:12,839
Kindly have a look.

71
00:05:17,640 --> 00:05:18,320
Mr. Wang.

72
00:05:18,839 --> 00:05:20,399
About the shares
you're transferring to me,

73
00:05:20,399 --> 00:05:21,399
I'll give you an extra percentage

74
00:05:21,720 --> 00:05:22,960
[Shares Transfer Agreement]
based on the market price.

75
00:05:24,359 --> 00:05:25,239
Besides,

76
00:05:25,559 --> 00:05:27,880
I've prepared a gift for your wife.

77
00:05:28,559 --> 00:05:29,959
Please open it.

78
00:05:43,399 --> 00:05:45,519
You don't have much time left.

79
00:05:46,600 --> 00:05:47,959
Your wife will be reaching here

80
00:05:48,480 --> 00:05:50,200
in a minute.

81
00:05:50,480 --> 00:05:51,239
No.

82
00:05:51,880 --> 00:05:52,920
58.

83
00:05:53,480 --> 00:05:54,600
57.

84
00:05:55,920 --> 00:05:57,119
56.

85
00:05:58,279 --> 00:05:59,600
55.

86
00:06:00,799 --> 00:06:02,079
54.

87
00:06:03,000 --> 00:06:04,679
Ten,

88
00:06:04,920 --> 00:06:05,920
nine,

89
00:06:06,880 --> 00:06:08,000
eight,

90
00:06:08,920 --> 00:06:10,040
seven,

91
00:06:11,239 --> 00:06:12,079
six,

92
00:06:13,679 --> 00:06:14,279
five...

93
00:06:14,279 --> 00:06:15,200
Fine.

94
00:06:38,480 --> 00:06:39,519
Are you Mrs. Wang?

95
00:06:40,200 --> 00:06:41,839
Ms. Yan prepared this for you.

96
00:06:47,839 --> 00:06:49,239
This seems pretty nice.

97
00:06:49,799 --> 00:06:51,040
Quite expensive, right?

98
00:06:51,399 --> 00:06:52,359
Yes, quite.

99
00:06:54,000 --> 00:06:55,160
Several hundred million.

100
00:07:00,119 --> 00:07:01,279
Dear guests,

101
00:07:02,000 --> 00:07:03,079
any objections?

102
00:07:03,990 --> 00:07:06,140
[In loving memory]

103
00:07:06,480 --> 00:07:07,279
[Chu Xin]
If no...

104
00:07:07,280 --> 00:07:08,160
[youngest daughter of the Chu family]
Yes.

105
00:07:10,799 --> 00:07:12,279
Who's she? What is she doing here?

106
00:07:12,640 --> 00:07:13,399
What's going on?

107
00:07:13,440 --> 00:07:14,119
What happens?

108
00:07:20,070 --> 00:07:22,250
[Anshi Group]

109
00:07:27,880 --> 00:07:28,799
I didn't know

110
00:07:29,000 --> 00:07:30,679
you had become the largest shareholder.

111
00:07:31,480 --> 00:07:32,119
Xin.

112
00:07:32,440 --> 00:07:34,000
Thank you for bringing Zejia here.

113
00:07:34,079 --> 00:07:34,519
After this press conference...

114
00:07:34,519 --> 00:07:35,119
Drop your act.

115
00:07:35,399 --> 00:07:37,079
You won't get a single dime
from the Chu family.

116
00:07:38,160 --> 00:07:39,920
Anshi Furniture contributed

117
00:07:39,920 --> 00:07:41,559
30 percent of the group's cash flow.

118
00:07:42,600 --> 00:07:44,040
Madam Chu wouldn't take your side

119
00:07:44,320 --> 00:07:45,640
even if she were here today.

120
00:07:45,679 --> 00:07:46,480
I don't care.

121
00:07:47,000 --> 00:07:47,959
Your achievements so far

122
00:07:48,320 --> 00:07:49,880
should be all thanks to the shares
my brother gave you.

123
00:07:50,119 --> 00:07:50,799
Yes.

124
00:07:51,440 --> 00:07:52,799
I toiled to run the company

125
00:07:53,239 --> 00:07:54,920
because I didn't want
to ruin his effort.

126
00:07:55,480 --> 00:07:56,920
I hope to give him a better Anshi

127
00:07:57,600 --> 00:07:59,359
when he returns.

128
00:07:59,360 --> 00:08:00,540
[Gu Cheng, marketing director,
Yan Zhen's childhood friend]

129
00:08:00,559 --> 00:08:01,559
But it's been four years.

130
00:08:02,399 --> 00:08:03,519
I have to accept the truth

131
00:08:03,720 --> 00:08:05,040
even though I hate it so much.

132
00:08:05,839 --> 00:08:06,519
So,

133
00:08:07,200 --> 00:08:08,799
I'd like to make an announcement here.

134
00:08:09,239 --> 00:08:09,920
Today,

135
00:08:11,000 --> 00:08:12,760
I officially declare the death

136
00:08:13,279 --> 00:08:14,160
of my husband,

137
00:08:15,119 --> 00:08:16,559
Chu Zejia.

138
00:08:20,239 --> 00:08:21,679
Xin, let's go home. Stop it already.

139
00:08:22,480 --> 00:08:24,799
Who are you to decide his death?

140
00:08:25,160 --> 00:08:27,160
You know better
whether it was an accident or not.

141
00:08:27,160 --> 00:08:28,839
Xin, come down. Don't make a scene here.

142
00:08:28,839 --> 00:08:29,640
If I had known

143
00:08:30,519 --> 00:08:32,159
that something was amiss

144
00:08:32,440 --> 00:08:33,520
behind Mr. Chu Jr.'s disappearance,

145
00:08:33,760 --> 00:08:35,440
I wouldn't have transferred my shares

146
00:08:35,840 --> 00:08:36,919
to Yan Zhen.

147
00:08:36,919 --> 00:08:38,039
You declared the death of Chu Zejia...

148
00:08:38,479 --> 00:08:39,400
Please give your comments.

149
00:08:39,719 --> 00:08:40,719
Please excuse us.

150
00:08:40,719 --> 00:08:42,559
The accident happened
on the day of your wedding anniversary.

151
00:08:42,559 --> 00:08:44,039
Why were you not on the boat?

152
00:08:44,039 --> 00:08:45,400
We won't make any comments today.

153
00:08:47,159 --> 00:08:48,119
Excuse me.

154
00:08:49,440 --> 00:08:50,599
Make way, please.

